《'''R'''》（風格化為《'''-R-'''》）是韓裔紐西蘭歌手兼[[BLACKPINK|BLACKPINK]]成員[[Rosé_(韓裔紐西蘭歌手)|Rosé]]的首張個人[[单曲#韓國|單曲專輯]]。本專輯由[[YG娛樂|YG娛樂]]和[[新視鏡唱片|新視鏡唱片]]發行，於3月4日開放預購，並於2021年3月12日正式發行販售<ref name="pre-order">{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000894513|title=블랙핑크 로제, 오늘(4일) 싱글 1집 'R' 예약 판매 시작|author=Jeong|first=Hee-yeon|date=2021-03-04|accessdate=2021-03-05|work=[[Naver|Naver]]|archivedate=2021-03-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304055609/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000894513}}</ref>。此專輯由Jon Bellion、ojivolta、Jorgen Odegard、[[泰迪·朴|泰迪]]、24和Brian Lee製作。 《R》主要是由[[合成器流行|合成器流行]]，[[流行舞曲|流行舞曲]]，[[電子流行|電子流行]]， [[電子舞曲|電子舞曲]] ，[[另类摇滚|另类摇滚]]，[[軟式搖滾|軟搖滾]]，[[独立摇滚|独立摇滚]]和[[摇滚乐|摇滚乐]]元素組成的的[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行音樂]]。專輯實體版銷售量在韓國[[Gaon音乐榜|Gaon音乐榜]]專輯排行榜上排名第2。

〈[[On_the_Ground|On the Ground]]〉作为專輯主打單曲發行。這首單曲在韓國排名第4，在美國[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百大單曲榜]]上排名第70，為韓國女性個人歌手作品的最高名次，這首歌也在[[告示牌全球二百大單曲榜|《告示牌》全球二百大單曲榜]]和[[公告牌全球二百强单曲榜|《告示牌》美國除外全球單曲榜]]上空降冠軍第1位，是首個同時空降雙榜冠軍的韓國個人歌手作品。副主打單曲〈[[Gone_(Rosé歌曲)|Gone]]〉於2021年4月5日公開音樂錄影帶。

== 背景 ==
2020年6月2日，[[YG娛樂|YG娛樂]]宣布将在[[BLACKPINK|Blackpink]]發行團體首張完整專輯後，於2020年年底讓Rosé以個人歌手身份出道發行專輯<ref>{{Cite news|title=YG, "ROSÉ·LISA·JISOO Will Release Solo Tracks… Will Start Releasing in Sequential Order After the Release of BLACKPINK's Full-Length Album in September"|url=https://yg-life.com/archives/155667?lang=en|accessdate=2020-01-25|agency=YG Entertainment|publisher=YG Entertainment|date=2020-06-02|archivedate=2020-07-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702100944/https://yg-life.com/archives/155667?lang=en}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=[공식입장] YG "블랙핑크, 로제·리사·지수 솔로곡 낸다…9월 정규앨범 이후 순차 발표"|url=http://www.mydaily.co.kr/new_yk/html/read.php?newsid=202006010910858499|accessdate=2021-03-02|work=My Daily|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010110722/http://mydaily.co.kr/new_yk/html/read.php?newsid=202006010910858499|archivedate=2020-10-10}}</ref> 。2020年12月30日，Rosé在接受韓國媒體Osen的採訪時透露，她將於2021年1月中旬拍攝個人出道單曲的音樂錄影帶<ref>{{Cite web|title=[단독] 블랙핑크 로제, 드디어 솔로출격..1월중순 뮤비 촬영 '콘서트+앨범준비 열일'|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/ranking/article/109/0004332667|accessdate=2020-12-30|work=Osen|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230064301/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/ranking/article/109/0004332667|archivedate=2020-12-30}}</ref> 。2021年1月25日，Blackpink的[[YouTube|YouTube]]官方頻道公開了一支名為 《Coming Soon》的33秒預告片，其中Rosé演唱了一段未知曲目<ref>{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Teases Her Solo Music Ahead of Their Livestream Concert|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9515892/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-project-teaser-video/|accessdate=2021-03-03|author=Mamo|date=2021-01-25|first=Heran|work=Billboard|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126010841/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9515892/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-project-teaser-video|archivedate=2021-01-26}}</ref> 。該預告片於發布24小時內突破1324萬觀賞次數，打破韓國女性個人歌手預告片紀錄<ref>{{Cite web|title=CELEBRITYBLACKPINK is said to be not popular in America, but Rosé’s teaser ranking is extremely high, and Knet also confirmed that Rosé’s voice has raised the level of the song.|url=https://kbizoom.com/blackpink-is-said-to-be-not-popular-in-america-but-roses-teaser-ranking-is-extremely-high-and-knet-also-confirmed-that-roses-voice-has-raised-the-level-of-the-song|accessdate=2021-04-04|publisher=kbizoom.com|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228153756/https://kbizoom.com/blackpink-is-said-to-be-not-popular-in-america-but-roses-teaser-ranking-is-extremely-high-and-knet-also-confirmed-that-roses-voice-has-raised-the-level-of-the-song}}</ref>。唱片公司YG娛樂透露，Rosé「在1月中旬完成了她個人專輯曲目的音樂錄影帶的所有拍攝工作」且發行的內容「肯定會和Blackpink常有的音樂風格不同」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Blackpink go solo: which member is releasing what, when|url=https://www.scmp.com/magazines/style/celebrity/article/3120921/blackpink-go-solo-roses-gone-was-highlight-show-will-lisa|accessdate=2021-03-03|author=Jeong|date=2021-02-08|first=Lucy|work=South China Morning Post|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302091727/https://www.scmp.com/magazines/style/celebrity/article/3120921/blackpink-go-solo-roses-gone-was-highlight-show-will-lisa|archivedate=2021-03-02}}</ref>。不久後，Rosé宣布將於2021年1月31日，也就是Blackpink的首次線上演唱會《[[BLACKPINK演唱會列表#BLACKPINK：THE_SHOW|The Show》]]上表演該預告片裡的曲目<ref name="theshow2">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Reveals Solo Debut Release Date|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date|accessdate=2021-03-03|date=2021-03-01|work=Billboard|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302050510/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date/|archivedate=2021-03-02}}</ref>。1月31日，Rosé於演唱會《The Show》表演該曲，一半為影像、一半為現場演唱，並正式確認該曲名為《[[Gone_(Rosé歌曲)|Gone]]》，其音源與影像片段遭大規模網路洩露。

2021年3月2日，[[YG娛樂|YG娛樂]]上傳了一張預告片海報，上面標有專輯名稱，並宣布了發行日期，正式宣佈將於3月12日啟動Rosé備受期待的個人出道活動<ref name="theshow">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Reveals Solo Debut Release Date|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date|accessdate=2021-03-03|date=2021-03-01|work=Billboard|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302050510/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date/|archivedate=2021-03-02}}</ref>。3月3日，新預告片海報首次揭開主打單曲《[[On_the_Ground|On the Ground]]》<ref name="Dork 1">{{Cite news|url=https://readdork.com/news/blackpinks-rose-is-set-to-release-her-debut-solo-single-on-the-ground-next-week/|title=Blackpink's Rosé is set to release her debut solo single 'On The Ground' next week|author=Philips|first=Lucy|date=2021-03-04|accessdate=2021-03-05|work=[[Dork_(magazine)|Dork]]|archivedate=2021-03-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304192943/https://readdork.com/news/blackpinks-rose-is-set-to-release-her-debut-solo-single-on-the-ground-next-week/}}</ref> <ref name="#1">{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/438/0000033577|title=블랙핑크 로제 솔로 컴백 'On The Ground'|author=Ji Eun|first=Jung|date=2021-03-04|accessdate=2021-03-05|work=Naver|archivedate=2021-03-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305035827/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/438/0000033577}}</ref> ，顯示與先前預告片揭露的《Gone》為不同歌曲。3月4日，Rosé首張個人單曲專輯開放網路預購<ref name="#2">{{Cite web|title=ROSÉ’s First Solo Album Pre-Order Event|url=https://m.en.ygselect.com/board/event/read.html?no=445972&board_no=12}}</ref>。3月7日，發布首支《On the Ground》音樂錄影帶預告片<ref name="#3">{{Cite web|title=Rosé - 'On The Ground' M/V Teaser|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_W8y2A9sK6s|accessdate=2021-03-07|author=|date=2021-03-07|first=|publisher=Blackpink|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307163446/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_W8y2A9sK6s|archivedate=2021-03-07}}</ref> <ref name="#4">{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/112/0003407219|title=블랙핑크 로제, 솔로곡 'On The Ground' 뮤비 티저 공개..우아美 폭발|author=Hye-yeon|first=Jeong|date=2021-03-08|accessdate=2021-03-08|work=Naver|archivedate=2021-03-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308021147/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/112/0003407219}}</ref> <ref name="#5">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-album-teaser-release-date-2891941|title=Blackpink's Rosé shares video teaser for upcoming solo single, 'On The Ground'|author=Ramli|first=Sofiana|date=2021-03-08|accessdate=2021-03-08|work=[[NME|NME]]|archivedate=2021-03-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305004708/https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-album-teaser-release-date-2891941}}</ref>。3月8日，YG公開專輯單曲目清單，確認收錄《Gone》與《On the Ground》兩首歌，並顯示Rosé參與了兩首歌的作詞與作曲<ref name=":02">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Gets Fancy for 'On the Ground' Music Video Teaser|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9536690/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-music-video-teaser/|accessdate=2021-03-09|date=2021-03-08|work=Billboard|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309055859/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9536690/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-music-video-teaser/|archivedate=2021-03-09}}</ref> 。3月9日，發表《On the Ground》的第二支音樂錄影帶預告片<ref name="#6">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-album-teaser-release-date-2891941|title=Blackpink's Rosé shares new video teaser for upcoming solo single, 'On The Ground'|author=Ramli|first=Sofiana|date=2021-03-10|accessdate=2021-03-10|work=NME|archivedate=2021-03-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305004708/https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-album-teaser-release-date-2891941}}</ref>。3月11日，Rosé在線上新聞發表會上透露，副主打《Gone》是兩年前就錄製好的，主打歌《On the Ground》則是近期才錄製的。

3月12日，《On the Ground》音樂錄影帶正式公開，兩首收錄曲的數位音源正式公開。實體專輯開始出貨與販售。3月13日，公開《On the Ground》幕後花絮，並於3月23日上傳舞蹈練習影片<ref name="#7">{{Cite web|title=Rosé Dances 'On the Ground' for Laid-Back Performance Video|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9544966/rose-on-the-ground-dance-performance-video/|accessdate=2021-03-23|author=Lee|date=2021-03-23|first=Cydney|work=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324160521/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9544966/rose-on-the-ground-dance-performance-video/|archivedate=2021-03-24}}</ref>。3月18日，Rosé公開個人YouTube頻道，上傳了採訪影片，結合成長影像紀錄，闡述本次主打曲概念<ref>{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK成員ROSÉ開設YouTube頻道 公開童年時期面貌|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/|accessdate=2021-03-18|work=yahoo.com|dead-url=no|archive-date=2018-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180926184140/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/}}</ref>。4月5日，YG娛樂公開了《Gone》的完整音樂錄影帶。

== 歌曲構成 ==
「我相信每一首歌都有最適合它的語言。針對主打歌用哪一種語言寫最適合，我掙扎了很久，但最後我認為是英文比較適合。說實在的，我很擔心粉絲會因為是英文歌詞而感到失望，但我認為呈現一首完整的、最好的、我自己滿意的歌曲，是很重要的。」- Rosé 於[[新音乐快递|新音樂快遞]]談及《R》的英文歌詞<ref>{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK’s Rosé takes things back to basics on captivating solo debut, ‘R’|url=https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312110231/https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194}}</ref>。

音樂性上，《R》主要是由[[合成器流行|合成器流行]]，[[流行舞曲|流行舞曲]]，[[電子流行|電子流行]]， [[電子舞曲|EDM]] ，[[另类摇滚|另類搖滾]]，[[軟式搖滾|軟搖滾]]，[[独立摇滚|獨立搖滾]]和[[摇滚乐|搖滾]]元素組成的的[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行音樂]]<ref name="Rolling Stones">{{Cite news|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-fallon-1143142/|title=Blackpink’s Rosé Breezes Through Elaborate ‘On the Ground’ Performance on ‘Fallon|author=Blistein|first=Jon|date=2021-03-17|accessdate=2021-03-18|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|archivedate=2021-03-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317193615/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-fallon-1143142/}}</ref> <ref name="Teen Vogue">{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé Drops "On the Ground" Music Video, New Song "Gone"|url=https://www.teenvogue.com/story/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-music-video-new-song-gone|accessdate=2021-03-13|author=Myer|date=2021-03-12|first=Maddy|work=[[Teen_Vogue|Teen Vogue]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312201045/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-music-video-new-song-gone|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref> <ref name="NME review">{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé takes things back to basics on captivating solo debut, 'R'|url=https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Daly|date=2021-03-12|first=Rhian|work=[[NME|NME]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312110231/https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref> <ref name="Young Hollywod">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Shows Off Her Growth as an Artist with 2-Track Solo EP 'R'!|url=https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|accessdate=2021-03-17|author=Murray|date=2021-03-16|first=Madison|work=[[Rolling_Stone_India|Rolling Stone India]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316211315/https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|archivedate=2021-03-16}}</ref> <ref name="Rolling Stone India">{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé Makes Solo Debut With Poignant 'On The Ground'|url=https://rollingstoneindia.com/blackpinks-rose-makes-solo-debut-with-poignant-on-the-ground/|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Dongre|date=2021-03-12|first=Divyansha|work=[[Rolling_Stone_India|Rolling Stone India]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314133304/https://rollingstoneindia.com/blackpinks-rose-makes-solo-debut-with-poignant-on-the-ground/|archivedate=2021-03-14}}</ref>。這張單曲專輯總長6分鐘15秒，共收錄兩首歌曲<ref name="Apple Music">{{Cite web|title=R - Single by Rosé|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/r-single/1557744841|accessdate=2021-03-14|date=2021-03-12|work=Apple Music|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312232605/http://music.apple.com/us/album/r-single/1557744841|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref>。[[新音乐快递|新音樂快遞]]觀察到「Rosé回歸最基本的元素上，去除那些她所屬的女子團體的作品裡，那些常使樂曲變得雜亂無章的過多層次；她選擇這首歌真正需要的元素，並採用一種安靜、柔和的方式來創作。」

在一場線上新聞發表會上，Rosé表示在進行自己投入了很多，在她首個個人出道專案上<ref name="Nylon">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/blackpink-rose-solo-album-r-details|title=BLACKPINK'S ROSÉ WILL REINTRODUCE HERSELF WITH SOLO EFFORT 'R'|author=Bell|first=Crystal|date=2021-03-12|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=[[Nylon|Nylon]]|archivedate=2021-03-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314200947/https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/blackpink-rose-solo-album-r-details}}</ref> 。她說：「由於我的粉絲已經等了這麼久，我希望它能令人滿意」、「從專輯的封面設計到我的第一首歌曲創作，我參加了很多會議來表達我對專輯的看法」 在實體專輯小冊子裡的製作人員名單中，可見Rosé與Teddy Park並列為整個專輯的創意總監。她表示在錄製唱片時，她回想起自己作為團員剛出道時的心境和對音樂的熱情：「我進行了反思，並意識到我有多愛音樂，得到安慰並與之一起成長。我以英語寫這首歌，因為我認為這是最適合它們的語言。我希望它們能使聽眾感到安慰」這位歌手還透露，她在兩年前第一次錄製了《[[Gone_(Rosé歌曲)|Gone]]》，而《[[On_the_Ground|On the Ground]]》「是最近才錄製的 」<ref name="Nylon" /> 。在Zach Sang節目專訪上，Rosé透露其實她從三年前就已經為個人出道計畫寫歌<ref name=":2" />。

=== 歌曲 ===
單曲專輯以《On the Ground》展開，一首[[電子音樂|電音]]和[[流行歌曲|流行歌曲]]，帶有[[合成器流行|合成流行]]元素和[[電子舞曲|電子舞曲]]風格的節拍，並配有簡單的吉他旋律<ref name="Young Hollywod2">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Shows Off Her Growth as an Artist with 2-Track Solo EP 'R'!|url=https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|accessdate=2021-03-17|author=Murray|date=2021-03-16|first=Madison|work=[[Rolling_Stone_India|Rolling Stone India]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316211315/https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|archivedate=2021-03-16}}</ref> <ref name="Rolling Stone India2">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Makes Solo Debut With Poignant 'On The Ground'|url=https://rollingstoneindia.com/blackpinks-rose-makes-solo-debut-with-poignant-on-the-ground/|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Dongre|date=2021-03-12|first=Divyansha|work=[[Rolling_Stone_India|Rolling Stone India]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314133304/https://rollingstoneindia.com/blackpinks-rose-makes-solo-debut-with-poignant-on-the-ground/|archivedate=2021-03-14}}</ref> <ref name="Rolling Stones2">{{Cite news|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-fallon-1143142/|title=Blackpink’s Rosé Breezes Through Elaborate ‘On the Ground’ Performance on ‘Fallon|author=Blistein|first=Jon|date=2021-03-17|accessdate=2021-03-18|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|archivedate=2021-03-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317193615/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-fallon-1143142/}}</ref> 。這首單曲帶有細膩與旋律性的主歌，伴隨帶有氣息的人聲與[[副歌|副歌]]，緊接著[[流行舞曲|流行舞曲]]式的編曲，天使般的橋接，並以末尾Rosé的高音作結<ref name="NME review2">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé takes things back to basics on captivating solo debut, 'R'|url=https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Daly|date=2021-03-12|first=Rhian|work=[[NME|NME]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312110231/https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref> <ref name="Teen Vogue2">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Drops "On the Ground" Music Video, New Song "Gone"|url=https://www.teenvogue.com/story/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-music-video-new-song-gone|accessdate=2021-03-13|author=Myer|date=2021-03-12|first=Maddy|work=[[Teen_Vogue|Teen Vogue]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312201045/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-music-video-new-song-gone|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref>。在這首歌裡，Rosé反思了她作为全球[[韓國流行音樂|K-pop]]超級巨星的生活，並意識到生活中真正重要的事情，已經存在於自己之中。

第二首曲目《Gone》是以電吉他為基礎的[[軟式搖滾|軟搖滾]]、[[另类摇滚|另類搖滾]]和[[独立摇滚|獨立搖滾]][[谣曲|抒情搖曲]]。為營造柔和的氣氛，這首歌的製作使用了不插電的聲音，並以刷弦方式彈奏吉他和弦<ref name="Teen Vogue3">{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé Drops "On the Ground" Music Video, New Song "Gone"|url=https://www.teenvogue.com/story/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-music-video-new-song-gone|accessdate=2021-03-13|author=Myer|date=2021-03-12|first=Maddy|work=[[Teen_Vogue|Teen Vogue]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312201045/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/blackpink-rose-on-the-ground-music-video-new-song-gone|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref> <ref name="Rolling Stone India3">{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé Makes Solo Debut With Poignant 'On The Ground'|url=https://rollingstoneindia.com/blackpinks-rose-makes-solo-debut-with-poignant-on-the-ground/|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Dongre|date=2021-03-12|first=Divyansha|work=[[Rolling_Stone_India|Rolling Stone India]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314133304/https://rollingstoneindia.com/blackpinks-rose-makes-solo-debut-with-poignant-on-the-ground/|archivedate=2021-03-14}}</ref> <ref name="NME review3">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé takes things back to basics on captivating solo debut, 'R'|url=https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Daly|date=2021-03-12|first=Rhian|work=[[NME|NME]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312110231/https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref> <ref name="Vulture2">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Goes Soló With R|url=https://www.vulture.com/2021/03/blackpink-rose-solo-r-on-the-ground-video.html|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Curto|date=2021-03-12|first=Justin|work=[[Vulture_(magazine)|Vulture]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312155925/https://www.vulture.com/2021/03/blackpink-rose-solo-r-on-the-ground-video.html|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref>。這首歌是一首令人心碎的分手歌，講述對已離開的前任的情緒<ref name="Young Hollywod3">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Shows Off Her Growth as an Artist with 2-Track Solo EP 'R'!|url=https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|accessdate=2021-03-17|author=Murray|date=2021-03-16|first=Madison|work=[[Young_Hollywood|Young Hollywood]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316211315/https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|archivedate=2021-03-16}}</ref>。

== 概念與標題 ==
一份新聞稿說，專輯的標題「不僅象徵Rosé名字的首字母，而且象徵著她作為個人歌手藝術家的新起點 <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-album-teaser-release-date-2891941|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé unveils title of lead single from upcoming solo album|author=Ramil|first=Sofiana|date=2021-03-05|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=[[NME|NME]]|archivedate=2021-03-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305004708/https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-rose-debut-solo-album-teaser-release-date-2891941}}</ref>。」她在一次全球新聞發表會上說：「許多人用很多名字稱呼我，所以「R」來自我名字的第一個字母，它代表了我獨唱的開始」，「我希望人們不是用『R』這個字母來定義我，而是在看到我的時候想到了『R』<ref name="Nylon">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/blackpink-rose-solo-album-r-details|title=BLACKPINK'S ROSÉ WILL REINTRODUCE HERSELF WITH SOLO EFFORT 'R'|author=Bell|first=Crystal|date=2021-03-12|accessdate=2021-03-15|work=[[Nylon|Nylon]]|archivedate=2021-03-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314200947/https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/blackpink-rose-solo-album-r-details}}<cite class="citation news cs1" data-ve-ignore="true" id="CITEREFBell2021">Bell, Crystal (12 March 2021). [https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/blackpink-rose-solo-album-r-details "BLACKPINK'S ROSÉ WILL REINTRODUCE HERSELF WITH SOLO EFFORT 'R<span class="cs1-kern-right">'</span>"]. ''[[尼龙|Nylon]]''. [https://web.archive.org/web/20210314200947/https://www.nylon.com/entertainment/blackpink-rose-solo-album-r-details Archived] from the original on 14 March 2021<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">15 March</span> 2021</span>.</cite></ref> 。「《[[On_the_Ground|On the Ground]]》是追求成功與夢想的漫長而艱難的旅程」Rosé在歌曲裡講述了簡單的事情，而這些事情對人生更為重要，像是家庭、朋友、健康和個人的幸福，而不是每個人都喜歡吹噓的成功的標準<ref name=";01">{{Cite news|url=http://mosen.mt.co.kr/article/G1111538677#_enliple|title=브레이브걸스, '롤린' 역주행→'인기가요' 1위 등극..블랙핑크 로제 솔로 데뷔∙WayV 컴백 [종합]|author=Hoon See|first=Seung|date=2021-03-14|accessdate=2021-03-25|work=Osen|archivedate=2021-03-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329164842/https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosanskr.css#_enliple}}</ref>。Rosé在《[[Gone_(Rosé歌曲)|Gone]]》中演唱了最終離開她的艱難愛情以及她破碎的心。據她所述，每當錄製一首歌時，她會扮演一個或另一個角色。而在這裡，如她所言，她只是做自己 <ref name="Young Hollywod">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Shows Off Her Growth as an Artist with 2-Track Solo EP 'R'!|url=https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|accessdate=2021-03-17|author=Murray|date=2021-03-16|first=Madison|work=[[Rolling_Stone_India|Rolling Stone India]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316211315/https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|archivedate=2021-03-16}}</ref>。

在韓國音樂節目[[人气歌谣|人氣歌謠]]演出後，Rosé說《On the Ground》是那些「尋找生命意義的人創作的，這首歌也是關鍵問題的答案」，以「答案早在我們靈魂深處，而且沒有人應該從別的地方尋找它<ref name=";01">{{Cite news|url=http://mosen.mt.co.kr/article/G1111538677#_enliple|title=브레이브걸스, '롤린' 역주행→'인기가요' 1위 등극..블랙핑크 로제 솔로 데뷔∙WayV 컴백 [종합]|author=Hoon See|first=Seung|date=2021-03-14|accessdate=2021-03-25|work=Osen|archivedate=2021-03-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329164842/https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosanskr.css#_enliple}}</ref>」Rosé親自命名這首歌曲，並認為這是她演唱過的所有歌曲中，最成功的一句歌詞。這意味著Rosé所需的一切都在這裡、「在地上」，並且無須急著去某處追尋<ref name="Young Hollywod">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Shows Off Her Growth as an Artist with 2-Track Solo EP 'R'!|url=https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|accessdate=2021-03-17|author=Murray|date=2021-03-16|first=Madison|work=[[Rolling_Stone_India|Rolling Stone India]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316211315/https://younghollywood.com/scene/blackpink-s-rose-shows-off-her-growth-as-an-artist-with-2-track-solo-ep-r.html|archivedate=2021-03-16}}</ref>。

== 發表與宣傳 ==
2021年3月2日，[[YG娛樂|YG娛樂]]上傳了一張預告片海報，上面標有專輯名稱《R》，並宣布了發行日期，正式宣佈將於3月12日啟動Rosé備受期待的個人出道活動<ref name="theshow">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Reveals Solo Debut Release Date|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date|accessdate=2021-03-03|date=2021-03-01|work=Billboard|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302050510/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date/|archivedate=2021-03-02}}</ref>，並表示專輯可從3月4日起進行預購<ref name="pre-order">{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000894513|title=블랙핑크 로제, 오늘(4일) 싱글 1집 'R' 예약 판매 시작|author=Jeong|first=Hee-yeon|date=2021-03-04|accessdate=2021-03-05|work=[[Naver|Naver]]|archivedate=2021-03-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304055609/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000894513}}</ref>。

