=== 單曲 ===
《[[On_the_Ground|On the Ground]]》作為專輯《R》的主打單曲，與專輯本身於2021年3月12日發行<ref name="Rolling Stone India">{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé Makes Solo Debut With Poignant 'On The Ground'|url=https://rollingstoneindia.com/blackpinks-rose-makes-solo-debut-with-poignant-on-the-ground/|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Dongre|date=2021-03-12|first=Divyansha|work=[[Rolling_Stone_India|Rolling Stone India]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314133304/https://rollingstoneindia.com/blackpinks-rose-makes-solo-debut-with-poignant-on-the-ground/|archivedate=2021-03-14}}</ref> <ref name="NME review">{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé takes things back to basics on captivating solo debut, 'R'|url=https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|accessdate=2021-03-12|author=Daly|date=2021-03-12|first=Rhian|work=[[NME|NME]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312110231/https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-r-on-the-ground-gone-review-2899194|archivedate=2021-03-12}}</ref>。由韓莎敏（Han Sa-min）執導<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rosé - On The Ground|url=https://vimeo.com/523546256|accessdate=2021-03-16|date=2021-03-15|publisher=YG, Sa Min Han|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324160513/https://vimeo.com/523546256|archivedate=2021-03-24}}</ref>的音樂錄影帶在歌曲發行的同一天首播。影片公開後12小時後，達到2300萬次觀看，成為韓國個人歌手最快達到兩千萬觀覽量的音樂錄影帶<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rosé’s "On The Ground" Video Has Glam Fashion, Casual Record Breaking|url=https://www.wmagazine.com/culture/rose-on-the-ground-music-video-fashion|accessdate=2021-03-18|author=Munzenrieder|date=2021-03-12|first=Kyle|work=W Magazine|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315213508/https://www.wmagazine.com/culture/rose-on-the-ground-music-video-fashion|archivedate=2021-03-15}}</ref>。該影片在美國東部標準時間上午12:00首映，吸引了超過120萬人同時在線觀看，打破YouTube音樂錄影帶首映歷史紀錄<ref name="records">{{Cite web|title=로제 MV 1억뷰…신기록 행진ing [공식]|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/144/0000725022|accessdate=2021-03-20|author=Byung-gil|date=2021-03-20|first=Ahn|work=SportsTrend|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320010421/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/144/0000725022|archivedate=2021-03-20}}</ref>。24小時內，《On the Ground》達到4160萬次的觀看次數，成為YouTube上24小時內韓國個人歌手最快最高紀錄，打破了Psy以《Gentleman》音樂錄影帶拿下並維持近八年的紀錄。發行後七天，成為史上女性個人歌手最快達到1億次觀看的音樂錄影帶 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0004369516|accessdate=2021-03-16|author=Lee|date=2021-03-16|first=Seung-hoon|work=Osen|language=ko|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20210316084353/https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0004369516|archivedate=2021-03-16}}</ref>。這支MV在中國[[QQ音乐|QQ音樂]]MV巔峰榜上，也拿下了3月8日至3月21日期間的雙週冠軍<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=巅峰榜·MV|url=https://y.qq.com/portal/mv_toplist.html#t2=202111&t1=all&stat=y_new.toplist.menu.mv_toplist|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2020-01-21|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200121215055/https://y.qq.com/portal/mv_toplist.html%23t2=202003&t1=mainland&stat=y_new.toplist.menu.mv_toplist#t2=202111&t1=all&stat=y_new.toplist.menu.mv_toplist}}</ref>。

在美國，《On the Ground》首次亮相並於美國[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百大單曲榜]]上排名第70，成為韓國女性個人歌手作品拿下的最高名次<ref name="hot 100">{{Cite tweet|user=billboardcharts|number=1374084346068361217|title=#Rosé's "On The Ground" debuts at No. 70 on this week's #Hot100.|date=2021-03-22|access-date=2021-03-23}}</ref>。這首歌也在[[告示牌全球二百大單曲榜|告示牌全球二百大單曲榜]]和[[公告牌全球二百强单曲榜|告示牌美國除外全球兩百大單曲榜]]上拿下全球排名第1，是史上首位同時空降雙榜冠軍的韓國個人歌手單曲<ref name="billboard global 2002">{{Cite web|title=Rose's 'On the Ground' Blasts In Atop Both Billboard Global Charts|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9544420/rose-on-the-ground-debuts-number-one-global-charts/|accessdate=2021-03-22|author=Trust|date=2021-03-22|first=Gary|work=Billboard|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322222014/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9544420/rose-on-the-ground-debuts-number-one-global-charts/|archivedate=2021-03-22}}</ref>。這首歌發售後旋即在全球獲得9210萬次串流與2萬9千次全球下載量<ref name="billboard global 2002" />，並橫掃51國Apple [[iTunes|iTunes]]音樂下載排行榜冠軍<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rose of BLACKPINK sweeps iTunes charts in 51 nations with latest single|url=https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20210313001400315|accessdate=2021-04-04|date=2021-03-13|publisher=YONHANP News|archive-date=2021-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313053930/https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20210313001400315}}</ref>，打破韓國女性個人歌手紀錄。

《[[Gone_(Rosé歌曲)|Gone]]》作為專輯《R》的副主打單曲，與專輯本身於2021年3月12日發行<ref name="Rolling Stone India" /> <ref name="NME review" />。雖然1月31日Rosé曾在演唱會《[[BLACKPINK演唱會列表#BLACKPINK：THE_SHOW|The Show》]]預先表演該曲，其音源與影像片段已遭大規模網路洩露<ref name="theshow">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Reveals Solo Debut Release Date|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date|accessdate=2021-03-03|date=2021-03-01|work=Billboard|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302050510/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date/|archivedate=2021-03-02}}</ref>。發行後，這首歌仍在美國[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]][https://www.billboard.com/charts/billboard-korea-100 K-pop Hot 100] {{Wayback|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/billboard-korea-100 |date=20201010003032 }}上排名第五<ref>{{Cite news|title=Korea Kpop Hot 100 Chart|url=http://billboard.co.kr/main/news/view/602|accessdate=2021-03-24|work=Billboard|archivedate=2021-03-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324160528/https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:100,400,500,700,900}}</ref>，美國[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]][[公告牌数字歌曲榜|數位歌曲銷售榜]]上排名第15位<ref>{{Cite web|title=BLACKPINK's Rosé Goes on Emotional Roller Coaster in 'Gone'|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9551031/blackpink-rose-gone-music-video|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404234748/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9551031/blackpink-rose-gone-music-video/}}</ref>，並在[[公告牌全球二百强单曲榜|全球200强]]中排名第29位，以及在[[公告牌全球二百强单曲榜|全球200強美國除外榜排名第17位]] <ref name="billboard global 2003">{{Cite web|title=Rose's 'On the Ground' Blasts In Atop Both Billboard Global Charts|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9544420/rose-on-the-ground-debuts-number-one-global-charts/|accessdate=2021-03-22|author=Trust|date=2021-03-22|first=Gary|work=Billboard|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322222014/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/9544420/rose-on-the-ground-debuts-number-one-global-charts/|archivedate=2021-03-22}}</ref>。4月5日《Gone》推出正式完整音樂錄影帶，於1小時2分內獲得100萬個點讚，並在半天後於[[YouTube|YouTube]]達到1000萬次的觀看次數<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000901522|title=블랙핑크 로제 'Gone' 뮤비, 반나절 만에 1천만뷰|author=Hee-yeon|first=Jeong|date=2021-04-05|accessdate=2021-04-05|work=Sports Donga|language=ko|archivedate=2021-04-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405091002/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000901522}}</ref>。在中國QQ音樂MV巔峰榜上，《Gone》也拿下了4月5日至4月11日期間的冠軍<ref name=":1" />。

=== 現場表演 ===
2021年1月31日，Rosé在Blackpink的首次線上演唱會《[[BLACKPINK演唱會列表#BLACKPINK：THE_SHOW|The Show》]]演出了《[[Gone_(Rosé歌曲)|Gone]]》<ref name="theshow">{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rosé Reveals Solo Debut Release Date|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date|accessdate=2021-03-03|date=2021-03-01|work=Billboard|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302050510/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9532920/blackpink-rose-solo-debut-release-date/|archivedate=2021-03-02}}</ref>。2021年3月14日，Rosé首次在[[SBS|SBS]]的[[人氣歌謠|人氣歌謠]]現場表演了《Gone》和《[[On_the_Ground|On the Ground]]》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Blackpink's Rose says songs for debut solo album 'R' came like fate|url=https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20210312005451315?section=news|accessdate=2021-03-16|author=Lee|date=2021-03-12|first=Minji|work=Yonhap News Agency|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318052819/https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20210312005451315?section=news|archivedate=2021-03-18}}</ref>。3月16日，Rosé在[[吉米·法伦今夜秀|吉米·法輪《今夜秀》]]中表演了《On the Ground》。這是Rosé首次在美國電視台上獨演，也使她成為第一個在這個電視節目表演的韓國個人歌手<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000895661|title=블랙핑크 로제, 美 ‘지미 팰런쇼’ 출연 [공식]|author=Hyo-jin|first=Jeon|date=2021-03-10|accessdate=2021-03-11|work=Naver|archivedate=2021-03-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310024803/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/382/0000895661}}</ref>。3月30日，Rosé也於[[日本電視台|日本電視台]]節目SUKKIRI上接受採訪並表演了《On the Ground》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rosé sits down for interview on 'The Kelly Clarkson Show'|url=https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2021/03/30/entertainment/kpop/Ros-rose-blackpink/20210330181300337.html|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605180410/https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2021/03/30/entertainment/kpop/Ros-rose-blackpink/20210330181300337.html}}</ref>。從三月中至四月初，Rosé也持續在[[M_Countdown|M Countdown]]、[[Show!_音樂中心|Show! 音樂中心]]和[[人氣歌謠|人氣歌謠]]節目上表演<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/312/0000474677|title='엠카' 로제 vs 브레이브걸스, 1위 트로피 대결|author=So-won|first=Schin|date=2021-03-18|accessdate=2021-03-19|work=Naver|archivedate=2021-03-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324160509/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/312/0000474677}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/052/0001565045|title=임영웅, 로제·아이유 꺾고 '음악중심' 1위..."영웅시대 감사"|author=Seo-yeon|first=Ban|date=2021-03-20|accessdate=2021-03-20|work=Naver|archivedate=2021-03-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320084829/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/052/0001565045}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/108/0002941264|title=임영웅, 로제·아이유 꺾고 '음악중심' 1위..."영웅시대 감사"|author=Hae-seon|first=Han|date=2021-03-21|accessdate=2021-03-21|work=Naver|archivedate=2021-03-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324160521/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/108/0002941264}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/112/0003414894|title='음악중심' 로제, 아이유·임영웅 꺾고 1위.."테디 오빠 고마워"[종합]|author=Hye-jeon|first=Jeong|date=2021-03-27|accessdate=2021-03-28|work=Heraldpop|archivedate=2021-03-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327080248/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/112/0003414894}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/469/0000592051|title='인기가요' 블랙핑크 로제 "과분한 사랑 감사" 1위 소감|author=Han-byul|first=Jeong|date=2021-03-28|accessdate=2021-03-28|work=Heraldpop|archivedate=2021-03-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328081838/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/469/0000592051}}</ref>。

== 商業表現 ==
Rosé的首張個人單曲專輯在開放預購的四天内，拿下超過40萬張訂單，成為韓國女性個人歌手最暢銷的單曲專輯<ref>{{Cite web|title=블랙핑크 로제, 4일만 선주문량 40만장↑…女 솔로 최고 기록|url=https://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=202103091153292410|accessdate=2021-03-09|date=2021-03-09|work=Newsen|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309033635/https://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=202103091153292410|archivedate=2021-03-09}}</ref>。3月15日，《R》預購量已經超過50萬張。在500,000張預購訂單中，有400,000張來自CD，48,000張來自Kit版，52,000張来自[[密紋唱片|黑膠]]唱片<ref name="500k">{{Cite web|title=[공식] 로제 'R', 선주문만 50만|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/117/0003472977|accessdate=2021-03-15|author=Seungrok Lee|date=2021-03-15|work=MyDaily|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315085948/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/117/0003472977|archivedate=2021-03-15}}</ref>。

3月17日，韓國專輯銷量紀錄權威網站[https://www.hanteochart.com/#/ Hanteo] {{Wayback|url=https://www.hanteochart.com/#/ |date=20210605165414 }}公開紀錄，表示《R》實體專輯於2021年3月16日開售當天售出了282,674張，並在一週後的3月22日，累積了448,089張的銷售量，創下韓國女個人歌手的最高首日及首週銷售紀錄<ref>{{Cite web|title=연 예 블랙핑크 로제, K팝 女 솔로 아티스트 초동 판매량 신기록..압도적 인기|url=http://www.breaknews.com/792728|accessdate=2021-03-17|date=2021-03-17|work=BreakNews|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317033916/https://www.breaknews.com/792728|archivedate=2021-03-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Update: BLACKPINK’s Rosé Breaks Record Of Highest 1st-Week Album Sales For Female Soloist With “R”|url=https://www.soompi.com/article/1459639wpp/blackpinks-rose-breaks-record-of-highest-1st-week-album-sales-for-female-soloist-in-a-day-with-r|access-date=2021-04-07|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416220722/https://www.soompi.com/article/1459639wpp/blackpinks-rose-breaks-record-of-highest-1st-week-album-sales-for-female-soloist-in-a-day-with-r}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=로제, 솔로앨범 초동 44만장 집계…女 솔로 최고 기록|url=https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=016&aid=0001810969|accessdate=2021-03-23|author=Ko|date=2021-03-23|first=Seung-hee|work=Herald Kyungje|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329164909/https://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=016&aid=0001810969|archivedate=2021-03-29}}</ref>。該成績讓Rosé成為韓國首位實體銷量突破40萬張的女個人歌手；也是不分性別，韓國史上第四位首週銷量超越40萬張的個人歌手<ref name=":32">{{Cite web|title=ROSÉ Achieves a Miraculous Record of 400,000 Copies as a Female Solo, Receives Hanteo Chart Official Certificate "Officially acknowledged once again after BLACKPINK's new record...'New Record Collector' ROSÉ"|url=https://www.hanteonews.com/en/article/all?fc=19587|access-date=2021-04-08|archive-date=2021-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210408082643/https://www.hanteonews.com/en/article/all?fc=19587}}</ref>。

Hanteo並於韓國4月8日，頒發Rosé『新紀錄認證獎牌』與『銀認證獎牌』<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=ROSÉ Achieves a Miraculous Record of 400,000 Copies as a Female Solo, Receives Hanteo Chart Official Certificate "Officially acknowledged once again after BLACKPINK's new record...'New Record Collector' ROSÉ"|url=https://www.hanteonews.com/en/article/all?fc=19587|access-date=2021-04-08|archive-date=2021-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210408082643/https://www.hanteonews.com/en/article/all?fc=19587}}</ref>。在Gaon專輯排行榜上，《R》實體專輯最高排名第二、Kit版本排名第七名 <ref name="Gaon Album Chart">{{Cite web|title=Gaon Album Chart – Week 12, 2021|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=12&hitYear=2021&termGbn=week|accessdate=2021-03-25|work=[[Gaon_Music_Chart|Gaon Chart]]|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325020832/http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=12&hitYear=2021&termGbn=week|archivedate=2021-03-25}}</ref>。Rosé本人也因為這張專輯，於3月22日在Spotify突破700萬月收聽人數，成為月收聽人數最高的韓國女性個人歌手，更於4月8日成為首位突破1200萬月收聽人數的韓國個人歌手<ref>{{Cite web|title=ROSÉ：Spotify|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/3eVa5w3URK5duf6eyVDbu9|access-date=2021-04-05|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324193730/https://open.spotify.com/artist/3eVa5w3URK5duf6eyVDbu9}}</ref>。4月12日，韓國Gaon實體專輯銷量紀錄《R》截至當天已售52.17萬張，為韓國女性首位，且個人歌手中最快突破50萬張的紀錄<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rosé #1, IU Appears 7 Times, And More, Gaon’s Highest-Selling K-Pop Female Soloist|url=http://en.koreaportal.com/articles/48964/20210412/ros%C3%A9-1-iu-appears-7-times-more-gaon-s-highest.htm|date=2021-04-16|access-date=2021-04-16|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419032852/http://en.koreaportal.com/articles/48964/20210412/ros%C3%A9-1-iu-appears-7-times-more-gaon-s-highest.htm}}</ref>。

在中國，這張專輯也取得了成功。《R》在3月12日開售當天，在中國最大音樂串流媒體服務[[QQ音乐|QQ音樂]]上，空降其數位媒體『巔峰暢銷榜』日榜、周榜與年榜冠軍<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=QQ音樂：恭喜ROSÉ|url=https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4623718590973029|access-date=2021-04-08|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503093022/https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4623718590973029}}</ref>，亦在[[酷狗音乐|酷狗音樂]]與[[酷狗音乐|酷我音樂]]等中國其他主要音樂網站中排名第一<ref name="China sales">{{Cite web|title=로제 솔로곡, 中서도 터졌다...QQ뮤직 등 1위 석권|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/052/0001562768|accessdate=2021-03-15|author=Jo Hyun-joo|date=2021-03-15|work=YTN|language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317074355/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/052/0001562768|archivedate=2021-03-17}}</ref>。《R》在發售隔日，於QQ音樂的銷量突破80萬張，成為平台最快突破各項等級至拿下「鑽石唱片」認證的日韓歌手<ref>{{Cite web|title=ROSÉ《-R-》空降QQ音乐5榜一位...数专销量突破80万张！|url=https://www.sohu.com/a/455473924_267454|access-date=2021-04-08|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503093023/https://www.sohu.com/a/455473924_267454}}</ref>，並於發行兩天後賣出100萬張數位版專輯<ref>{{Cite web|title=QQ Music R Digital Downloads|url=https://y.qq.com/n/yqq/album/002alg1L0AVYZs.html#stat=y_new.singer.index.albumName|accessdate=2021-03-13|date=2021-03-13|work=[[QQ_Music|QQ Music]]|language=zh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314133415/https://y.qq.com/#stat=y_new.singer.index.albumName|archivedate=2021-03-14}}</ref>，截至4月8日，QQ音樂上的銷量突破1,350,000張，<ref name=":4" />，加上酷狗與酷我平台的銷量，總計超過1,500萬張，使Rosé成為QQ音樂及中國合計銷量最高的韓國個人歌手<ref name="#8">{{Cite web|title=酷狗音樂：ROSÉ《-R-》|url=http://zhuanjistatic.kugou.com/html/pc_commonchargeV3/index_378800.html|access-date=2021-04-20|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326223300/https://ep.kugou.com/dist/css/pc_commonchargeV3/index_63fede.css}}</ref><ref name="#9">{{Cite web|title=酷我音樂：ROSÉ《-R-》|url=http://vip1.kuwo.cn/fans/fans/template/index.html?key=rose210312|access-date=2021-04-20|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416001242/https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/zkd3alvsktoFJfjfkrKSEoVPyib1ibAqIHCNrrjNgDO3nQzvFwpfz0KicIrrYgXtSt8NicwRAn7tgaialD2HvzWt4sA/132}}</ref>。韓國Gaon實體專輯銷量紀錄公布，截至4月12日，《R》已售52.17萬張，為首位突破40與50萬張大關的韓國女個人歌手，亦為個人歌手中最快突破50萬張的紀錄<ref name=":132">{{Cite web|title=Rosé #1, IU Appears 7 Times, And More, Gaon’s Highest-Selling K-Pop Female Soloist|url=http://en.koreaportal.com/articles/48964/20210412/ros%C3%A9-1-iu-appears-7-times-more-gaon-s-highest.htm|access-date=2021-04-16|date=16 Apr 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419032852/http://en.koreaportal.com/articles/48964/20210412/ros%C3%A9-1-iu-appears-7-times-more-gaon-s-highest.htm|archive-date=2021-04-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月5日，《R》獲Gaon白金認證，Rosé為首次達成此紀錄的女個人歌手。據韓國《Vogue》報導，在2021年推出個人專輯的歌手中，Rosé的成績最為優異<ref>{{Cite web|title=빛이 나는 솔로 4（閃耀的4位個人歌手）|url=http://www.vogue.co.kr/2021/04/13/%eb%b9%9b%ec%9d%b4-%eb%82%98%eb%8a%94-%ec%86%94%eb%a1%9c-4/|access-date=2021-04-16|date=13 Apr 2021|publisher=韓國Vogue|language=ko|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413171930/http://www.vogue.co.kr/2021/04/13/%EB%B9%9B%EC%9D%B4-%EB%82%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%86%94%EB%A1%9C-4/|archive-date=2021-04-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月31日，YG娛樂更新數據顯示《R》在發售一個月內即售出62萬張<ref>{{Cite web|title=YG, 블랙핑크·트레저 고속 질주로 주가 6만원 넘본다|url=https://n.news.naver.com/mnews/article/016/0001841702?sid=101|access-date=2021-06-05|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605221953/https://n.news.naver.com/mnews/article/016/0001841702?sid=101}}</ref>。

